model = ComplexModelWith2List1Normal()
model.set(new=[1, 2], new2=[3, 4])
model.put()
sql = (
    'SELECT new, new2, new3 FROM simple_new_new2_new3_index WHERE simple_id = %s'
    )
result = Database.get().query(sql, model.get('id'))
self.assertEquals(len(result), 4)
expectedResult = [{'new': '1', 'new2': '3', 'new3': 'normal'}, {'new': '1',
    'new2': '4', 'new3': 'normal'}, {'new': '2', 'new2': '3', 'new3':
    'normal'}, {'new': '2', 'new2': '4', 'new3': 'normal'}]
self.assertEquals(result, expectedResult)
